{"tid":2129822,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（亮劍）中方決定：香港暫停與加、澳、英的逃犯移交協定","createTime":"2020-07-29T01:05:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-30T01:14:00.000Z","uid":43785,"like":24,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"9293a4b72cc2d9232209d399dd87228fe4269acb","tid":2129822,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T01:05:45.000Z","msg":"中方決定：香港暫停與加、澳、英的逃犯移交協定<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yqbVVXi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyqbVVXi.jpg&h=90a316dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在北京，外交部發言人汪文斌宣布，中方決定香港特區暫停與加拿大、澳洲和英國移交逃犯協定，同時暫停香港特區與三國的刑事司法互助協定。<br />\n<br />\n汪文斌表示，近日加拿大、澳洲和英國以中國製定《港區國安法》爲藉口，單方面宣布暫停與香港特區簽訂的移交逃犯協定，此舉粗暴干涉中國內政，嚴重違反國際法和國際關係基本準則，中方對此堅決反對。<br />\n<br />\n他指香港特區在中央政府協助和授權下，按基本法，在協定框架下，向加拿大、澳洲和英國提供積極協助，加拿大、澳洲和英國對香港司法合作政治化的錯誤行徑，嚴重損害香港與這些國家的司法合作基礎，偏離了司法合作，維護正義和法治宗旨。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中國亮劍了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n被制裁後反制英美加澳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中國好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係打飛機咁簡單，美國隱形戰機都俾你打穿了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d53bd5cd636184387181a35640d9407cf0211bc3","tid":2129822,"uid":312193,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T01:06:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M0UKuT1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM0UKuT1.gif&h=ea5ee1e7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a84404db